From 675a5dc4730d11984e2e13f6a61d8cbdf6aa7200 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dylan Gormley <dylan.gormley@mail.wvu.edu>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 20:39:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add tutorial slide deck and shared README figures

docs/presentation/ holds the 28-slide tutorial (Amurmaple + WVU color
theme, presenter notes throughout); build both PDFs with 'make slides'.
The figure vocabulary is factored into assets/datatrawl-figures.sty and
five shared bodies (assets/fig-*.tikz) that the deck inputs directly and
'make diagram' renders to the committed assets/fig-*.svg, now embedded
in the README at the matching sections.
